Proposed law provides that an employee cannot be discharged, demoted, suspended,
threatened, harassed, or discriminated against for obtaining a leave of absence to become a
human organ or bone marrow donor.
Proposed law provides that organ donor paid leave will not have cash value upon
termination.
Effective August 1, 2026.
